Method Detail

parse

public static void parse(net.minidev.json.JSONObject o,
                         Claim claim)
                  throws ParseException
Parses a claim value from the specified JSON object. Supports all claim JSON data types expect array and object.

Parameters:
o - The JSON object containing a member representing the parsed claim. Must not be null.
claim - The claim. Its value will be set to the value of the JSON member with the matching key (name). Must not be null.
Throws:
ParseException - If the JSON object doesn't contain a member with a matching key (name), its value is null or of unexpected type.
